#            Metasploit, Empire, and other red-team frameworks by:
#              - YAML-DEFINED TTPs — each TTP is a YAML file
#                specifying steps (basic / file / subttp / cleanup
#                step types), dependencies, success conditions,
#                and Mitre ATT&CK mappings
#              - TTP REPOSITORY MODEL — TTPs are bundled into
#                repositories (Git-backed) that ttpforge install/
#                remove manages locally; multiple repos can
#                coexist
