#                  * OsFs           — passes through to os.* calls
#                  * MemMapFs       — in-memory filesystem (ideal
#                                      for tests; no disk touch)
#                  * BasePathFs     — chroots an OsFs to a base path
#                  * ReadOnlyFs     — wraps an Fs as read-only
#                  * RegexpFs       — filters files by regex
#                  * HttpFs         — HTTP filesystem (read-only)
#                  * CopyOnWriteFs  — layered filesystem (overlay)
#                  * CacheOnReadFs  — cached reads on top of slow Fs
